Body: Description: We need to upgrade the server to the latest version to comply with the security recommendations, we could upgrade to 9.0.4 version but when the process finished we get the low disk space error again, before to proceed with the another upgrade we would like to clear up the alert to avoid a system problem during the update.
Next Steps Updated: Waiting on customer availability for next week to schedule RS.
What We've Learned Updated: Disk space issue. Cleared space on both disks.

Next Steps Updated: 27Jan: Waiting to close ticket.

Waiting on customer availability for next week to schedule RS.
